      <div>
        <h1 class="text">I'm from Paris</h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I live in modern-day Paris, I enjoy<br>coffee, the boulevards, and Saint-Germain.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Revolution runs through my veins, even if they<br>truly think it doesn’t.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Far away there’s an island where coffee ripens well,<br>where rumba is danced<br>even on one foot.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I speak French, Oui, s’il vous plaît.<br>I know nothing of that nation, I only know</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">you can hear an old street cry: Maní Maní,<br>my rich and warm peanuts.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">They say rum is sipped in every corner.<br>Could it be true that in Cuba they live in peace—</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">or in war, or perhaps in transition?<br>I will travel through time and break tradition.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I will get to know that place, they say they speak Spanish—<br>a very popular Spanish.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I only want to carry my true dream,<br>to suffer heartbreak for a mulata,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">to dance to the rhythm of a tin can,<br>to talk politics for a bit and then watch a salsa band.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I’m far away, I wonder what that country is like—<br>hard to discuss it before I’ve lived there.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Truth is different for each person,<br>let me discover a poor place where my brother lives,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">even if they call him Cuban, he’s a survivor,<br>and he shows his teeth out of courtesy<br>with each step you take.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I can’t leave my French accent behind,<br>but I can enrich myself, learn from universal culture,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">learn…<br>See from deep within: swim in both worlds,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">in one single voyage of faith.</p>
      </div>

